data.description: Welcome home to 9919 Sacate Blanco Ave! A newer built LGI home situated on a corner lot which includes a covered patio, a two-car garage, a spacious laundry room and tons of closet space. An open kitchen features energy-efficient appliances and is located between the living and dining rooms establishing an open floorplan. This home has been well maintained and shows light and bright. The floors have been upgraded to wood flooring! The master suite is made up of a large room with a view of the backyard, walk-in closet and private bath with separate shower and soaking tub. Rest assured this home is energy sufficiant with solar energy!  Schedule your showing today!
